Simsttab: A timetabling engine for schools

https://www.metalevel.at/simsttab/

Simsttab stands for Simplistic School Time-Tabler. 
It is a timetabling engine that can generate timetables satisfying requirements typical for secondary schools 
in Austria ("Gymnasium"-type), Germany and maybe other European countries.

Source code: simsttab.pl

Video:	School Timetabling with Prolog

The code is also available from a public git repository: https://github.com/triska/simsttab/

